#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.34"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.34:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.34:0.2"
msgid "4. Paṭipattivagga"
msgstr "4. Practice"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.34:0.3"
msgid "34. Pāraṅgamasutta"
msgstr "34. Going to the Far Shore"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.34:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn45.34:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Aṭṭhime, bhikkhave, dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā apārā pāraṃ gamanāya "
"saṃvattanti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when these eight things are developed and cultivated they lead "
"to going from the near shore to the far shore."

msgctxt "sn45.34:1.3"
msgid "Katame aṭṭha?"
msgstr "What eight?"

msgctxt "sn45.34:1.4"
msgid "Seyyathidaṃ—sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi."
msgstr ""
"They are right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right "
"livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion."

msgctxt "sn45.34:1.5"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭha dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā apārā pāraṃ gamanāya "
"saṃvattantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When these eight things are developed and cultivated they lead to going from "
"the near shore to the far shore.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.34:2.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "sn45.34:2.2"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvāna sugato athāparaṃ etadavoca satthā:"
msgstr "Then the Holy One, the Teacher, went on to say:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.34:3.1"
msgid "“Appakā te manussesu,"
msgstr "“Few are those among humans"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:3.2"
msgid "ye janā pāragāmino;"
msgstr "who cross to the far shore."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:3.3"
msgid "Athāyaṃ itarā pajā,"
msgstr "The rest just run"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:3.4"
msgid "tīramevānudhāvati."
msgstr "around on the near shore."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.34:4.1"
msgid "Ye ca kho sammadakkhāte,"
msgstr "When the teaching is well explained,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:4.2"
msgid "dhamme dhammānuvattino;"
msgstr "those who practice accordingly"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:4.3"
msgid "Te janā pāramessanti,"
msgstr "are the ones who will cross over"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:4.4"
msgid "maccudheyyaṃ suduttaraṃ."
msgstr "Death’s domain so hard to pass."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.34:5.1"
msgid "Kaṇhaṃ dhammaṃ vippahāya,"
msgstr "Rid of dark qualities,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:5.2"
msgid "sukkaṃ bhāvetha paṇḍito;"
msgstr "an astute person should develop the bright."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:5.3"
msgid "Okā anokamāgamma,"
msgstr "Leaving home behind"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:5.4"
msgid "viveke yattha dūramaṃ."
msgstr "for the seclusion so hard to enjoy,"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.34:6.1"
msgid "Tatrābhiratimiccheyya,"
msgstr "you should try to find delight there,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:6.2"
msgid "hitvā kāme akiñcano;"
msgstr "having left behind sensual pleasures."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:6.3"
msgid "Pariyodapeyya attānaṃ,"
msgstr "With no possessions, an astute person"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:6.4"
msgid "cittaklesehi paṇḍito."
msgstr "should cleanse themselves of mental corruptions."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.34:7.1"
msgid "Yesaṃ sambodhiyaṅgesu,"
msgstr "And those whose minds are rightly developed"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:7.2"
msgid "sammā cittaṃ subhāvitaṃ;"
msgstr "in the awakening factors;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:7.3"
msgid "Ādānapaṭinissagge,"
msgstr "letting go of attachments,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:7.4"
msgid "anupādāya ye ratā;"
msgstr "they delight in not grasping."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:7.5"
msgid "Khīṇāsavā jutimanto,"
msgstr "With defilements ended, brilliant,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn45.34:7.6"
msgid "te loke parinibbutā”ti."
msgstr "they are extinguished in this world.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.34:7.7"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
